<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Single Page Website</title>
    <style>
        /* Basic styling */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* Navigation Bar */
        nav {
            background-color: #383838;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        nav a {
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        /* Header section */
        header {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 20px;
            background-image: url('https://e0.pxfuel.com/wallpapers/263/621/desktop-wallpaper-green-blur.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            color: rgb(204, 250, 198);
            
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin: 0;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

        /* Main content section */
        section {
            padding: 60px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        section h2 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        section p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        /* Footer section */
        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px 0;
            position: relative;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
    <nav>
        <a href="#home">Home</a>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#services">Services</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        <a href="#">{{Username}}</a>
    </nav>

    <!-- Header Section -->
    <header id="home">
        <h1>About to {{Username}}</h1>
        <p>This is a about page</p>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content Section -->
    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>
            We are a leading web development company offering professional services to help businesses establish a strong online presence. Our team specializes in building custom websites tailored to the needs of our clients.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section id="services">
        <h2>Our Services</h2>
        <p>
            Our services include web design, web development, e-commerce solutions, SEO, and digital marketing. We are dedicated to providing top-notch solutions that help our clients succeed in the digital landscape.
        </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer Section -->
    <footer id="contact">
        <p>&copy; 2024 My Website. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
